Oh, wonderful...</span><hr size=1> I can see both sides of this - as Pahraith says, this could have some advantages to both level 60s and people just coming into their 50s.  I have two toons I play as well, my Bard at 60 and my Beastlord about to hit 47 - and it seems to me the overall result of these changes will be positive.  If this patch means I can zone into CT or UP or something and shout Bard LFG and have more than a snowball's chance in hell of actually getting something, then I'm all for it - it'd be nice to see a lot of the zones that are good xp for high 50s/60 that have until now been BYOG zones only to start becoming pickup zones to rival Seb/Velk's etc.  Will it happen?  Who knows, time will tell.<br>
<br>
Similarly, I agree with Pah's comment about looking for groups in the old xp zones - as a result of the easy accessibility of good gear at relatively low levels, it's easier than ever for low 50s groups to do well for themselves in Seb, Velk's etc, but the chances of such characters finding groups in those zones are severely impaired by the number of people AAing there.  I had initially intended to level my Beastlord solo til at least 54 or 55 before trying to group in those zones, simply because of the difficulty of finding groups.<br>
<br>
The effect on soloing, however, I do not like the sound of - up until now, soloing was for the most part slightly better xp than grouping, but in my mind that was made up for by the boredom of it, lack of social interaction (not that that is always a bad thing), and having to pay full attention.  Subsequently, I enjoyed being able to solo low blues from time to time to move my xp along a little - with this patch, that's essentially gone all to hell.  This is not such a big thing for classes who can solo or group, such as Bards, but I can see it being severely detrimental to classes who's post 50-lives largely revolved around soloing in the past, such as necros and druids.  I can't see this as being a good thing.<br>
<br>
And the hammer.. hopefully we will see that gone soon.. I can just see people /oocing 'Group looking for Rogue, Monk, Wizzy or Cleric'... <p><font size=1 face=arial color=#D5CA91>Benway, level 60 Troubadoobiedoo, Clan Bashemded  <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=338062">(My Stuffs)</a><br><br>"I must confess, I find it difficult to believe in... a disease of machinery"</font></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#00FFFF>- </font><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency>The Rathe Travel Agency Board</a><font color=#00FFFF> - </font><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm15>Flame Central</a> <font color=#00FFFF> - </font><a href="http://www.jakefitch.com/rta/Calendar.asp">The Rathe Calendar</a><font color=#00FFFF> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.0.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.<br>Accelerated By <a href=http://www.wbs.com/ezboard.html>JXEL</a></center></body></html>  

